{
  "stem": "11175.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I lived with that-- with the dreams from yesterday, not from today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Today was a very bad life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I started as soon as my father died, as soon as my mother married-- married the second time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My life, it started to get harder and harder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CRYING] But I thank God I survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I survived and I lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I lived in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then my mother lived in Demblin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You see my mother lived with that second husband in Demblin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then they decided they're going to move to Otwock-- that Otwock, it was a town-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But when I got older already, I came and I worked in Warsaw, and moving-- my mother is not-- said, look, I'm going to sleep over here, and I'm going to work in the town.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm going to have a ticket and go every day for the work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't make that everything, you know-- and I came every night, I had that ticket for a month, r for a week.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every night I came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I kept myself-- I didn't need my mother at that time, anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived-- my brother together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother and sister, the older ones, they never came home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And when I became-- when I got older, I came with this-- you know, this was already 18, 19 years, 20 years old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So now that's starting army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, at 21 years, I have to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I want you to-- I want you to know one thing, that until 21, until I was 20 years, I didn't know when I was born.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
